#: ml-slider.php:2072
msgid ""
"With Vimeo slides, you can build beautiful slideshows with your Vimeo "
"videos."
msgstr "Pẹlu Vimeo slides, o le kọ awọn slideshows ẹwa pẹlu awọn fidio Vimeo rẹ."

#: ml-slider.php:2076
msgid ""
"Vimeo slides will display your videos with auto play, mute, the ability to "
"hide controls, and much more."
msgstr ""
"Vimeo slides yoo han awọn fidio rẹ pẹlu ṣiṣere laifọwọyi, idakọ, agbara "
"lati pa awọn iṣakoso, ati pupọ diẹ sii."

#: ml-slider.php:2109
msgid "Create slideshows with your YouTube videos"
msgstr "Ṣẹda awọn slideshows pẹlu awọn fidio YouTube rẹ"

#: ml-slider.php:2113
msgid ""
"With YouTube slides, you can build beautiful slideshows with your YouTube "
"videos."
msgstr "Pẹlu YouTube slides, o le kọ awọn slideshows ẹwa pẹlu awọn fidio YouTube rẹ."

#: ml-slider.php:2117
msgid ""
"YouTube slides will display your videos with auto play, mute, lazy load, "
"the ability to hide controls, and much more."
msgstr ""
"YouTube slides yoo han awọn fidio rẹ pẹlu ṣiṣere laifọwọyi, idakọ, ikojọpọ "
"laisiyonu, agbara lati pa awọn iṣakoso, ati pupọ diẹ sii."

#: ml-slider.php:2150
msgid "Create slideshows with your posts"
msgstr "Ṣẹda awọn slideshows pẹlu awọn ifiweranṣẹ rẹ"

#: ml-slider.php:2154
msgid ""
"With Post Feed slides, you can build slideshows with your latest posts, "
"events, or WooCommerce products."
msgstr ""
"Pẹlu Post Feed slides, o le kọ awọn slideshows pẹlu awọn ifiweranṣẹ tuntun "
"rẹ, awọn iṣẹlẹ, tabi awọn ọja WooCommerce."

#: ml-slider.php:2158
msgid ""
"Post Feed slides will automatically display your posts with images, text, "
"custom fields, and much more."
msgstr ""
"Post Feed slides yoo han laifọwọyi awọn ifiweranṣẹ rẹ pẹlu awọn aworan, "
"ọrọ, awọn aaye aṣa, ati pupọ diẹ sii."

#: ml-slider.php:2193
msgid "Create slideshows with images stored outside of WordPress"
msgstr "Ṣẹda awọn slideshows pẹlu awọn aworan ti a fipamọ ni ita WordPress"

#: ml-slider.php:2197
msgid ""
"With External URL slides, you can load images directly from non-WordPress "
"sources such as CDNs or image hosts."
msgstr ""
"Pẹlu awọn slidẹs URL ita, o le gba awọn aworan taara lati awọn orisun ti "
"kii ṣe WordPress gẹgẹbi CDNs tabi awọn alejo aworan."

#: ml-slider.php:2201
msgid ""
"External URL slides give you all the power of MetaSlider Slideshow, using "
"images stored anywhere you want."
msgstr ""
"Awọn slidẹs URL ita fun ọ ni gbogbo agbara ti MetaSlider Slideshow, nipa "
"lilo awọn aworan ti a fipamọ nibikibi ti o fẹ."

#: ml-slider.php:2236
msgid "Create slideshows with videos in your media library"
msgstr "Ṣẹda awọn slidẹs pẹlu awọn fidio ninu ile-ikawe media rẹ"

#: ml-slider.php:2240
msgid ""
"With Local Video slides, you can build beautiful slideshows with videos in "
"your WordPress media library."
msgstr ""
"Pẹlu awọn slidẹs fidio agbegbe, o le kọ awọn slidẹs ẹwa pẹlu awọn fidio "
"ninu ile-ikawe media WordPress rẹ."

#: ml-slider.php:2244
msgid ""
"Local Video slides will display your MP4, WebM, and MOV videos with cover "
"images, auto play, mute, lazy load, the ability to hide controls, and much "
"more."
msgstr ""
"Awọn slidẹs fidio agbegbe yoo ṣafihan awọn fidio MP4, WebM, ati MOV rẹ pẹlu "
"awọn aworan bo, ṣiṣan laifọwọyi, pa, gbigbe laiyara, agbara lati pa awọn "
"iṣakoso, ati pupọ diẹ sii."

#: ml-slider.php:2279
msgid "Create slideshows with videos stored outside of WordPress"
msgstr "Ṣẹda awọn slidẹs pẹlu awọn fidio ti a fipamọ ni ita WordPress"

#: ml-slider.php:2283
msgid ""
"With External Video slides, you can add videos directly from non-WordPress "
"sources."
msgstr ""
"Pẹlu awọn slidẹs fidio ita, o le ṣafikun awọn fidio taara lati awọn orisun "
"ti kii ṣe WordPress."

#: ml-slider.php:2287
msgid ""
"External Video Slides will display your MP4, WebM, and MOV videos. Features "
"include text captions, cover images, auto play, mute, lazy load, the "
"ability to hide controls, and much more."
msgstr ""
"Awọn slidẹs Fidio Ita yoo ṣafihan awọn fidio MP4, WebM, ati MOV rẹ. Awọn "
"ẹya ara ẹrọ pẹlu awọn akọsilẹ ọrọ, awọn aworan bo, ṣiṣan laifọwọyi, pa, "
"gbigbe laiyara, agbara lati pa awọn iṣakoso, ati pupọ diẹ sii."

#: ml-slider.php:2322
msgid "Create slideshows with custom HTML"
msgstr "Ṣẹda awọn slidẹs pẹlu HTML aṣa"

#: ml-slider.php:2326
msgid ""
"With Custom HTML slides, you can design slides using images, HTML and CSS. "
"This gives you complete control over the layout and styling."
msgstr ""
"Pẹlu awọn slidẹs HTML aṣa, o le ṣe apẹrẹ awọn slidẹs nipa lilo awọn aworan, "
"HTML ati CSS. Eyi fun ọ ni iṣakoso pipe lori apẹrẹ ati aṣa."

#: ml-slider.php:2361
msgid "Create slideshows with Tiktok Videos"
msgstr "Ṣẹda awọn slidẹs pẹlu awọn fidio Tiktok"

#: ml-slider.php:2365
msgid ""
"A TikTok Slide will display a video in your slideshow directly from "
"TikTok.com."
msgstr "A TikTok Slide yoo ṣafihan fidio kan ninu slidẹ rẹ taara lati TikTok.com."

#: ml-slider.php:2428
msgid "Create slideshows with images from a folder"
msgstr "Ṣẹda awọn slidẹs pẹlu awọn aworan lati folda kan"

#: ml-slider.php:2432
msgid ""
"The Image Folder slide type extracts images from a specified folder and "
"displays them as slides."
msgstr ""
"Iru slidẹ Aworan Folda n fa awọn aworan lati folda ti a sọtọ ki o si "
"ṣafihan wọn gẹgẹbi awọn slidẹs."

#: ml-slider.php:2436
msgid ""
"This slide type displays images from folders in your WordPress Media "
"Library."
msgstr ""
"Iru slidẹ yii n ṣafihan awọn aworan lati awọn folda ninu Ile-ikawe Media "
"WordPress rẹ."

#: ml-slider.php:2463
msgid "Create slideshows with Post Images"
msgstr "Ṣẹda awọn slidẹs pẹlu Awọn Aworan Ifiweranṣẹ"

#: ml-slider.php:2467
msgid ""
"The Post Images slide type extracts images from the current post and "
"displays them as slides."
msgstr ""
"Iru slidẹ Awọn Aworan Ifiweranṣẹ n fa awọn aworan lati ifiweranṣẹ lọwọlọwọ "
"ki o si ṣafihan wọn gẹgẹ bi awọn slidẹs."

#: ml-slider.php:2471
msgid ""
"This slide type supports featured images, post content images, WooCommerce "
"galleries, Advanced Custom Fields images and galleries."
msgstr ""
"Iru slidẹ yii n ṣe atilẹyin awọn aworan ti a ṣe afihan, awọn aworan akoonu "
"ifiweranṣẹ, awọn ile-iṣẹ WooCommerce, awọn aworan aaye Atilẹba, ati awọn "
"ile-iṣẹ."

#: ml-slider.php:2498
msgid "Create slideshows with your WooCommerce products"
msgstr "Ṣẹda awọn slidẹs pẹlu awọn ọja WooCommerce rẹ"

#: ml-slider.php:2502
msgid ""
"With WooCommerce slides, you can build slideshows with your WooCommerce "
"products."
msgstr ""
"Pẹlu awọn slidẹs WooCommerce, o le kọ awọn slidẹs pẹlu awọn ọja WooCommerce "
"rẹ."

#: ml-slider.php:2506
msgid ""
"WooCommerce slides will automatically display your products with images, "
"text, custom fields, and much more."
msgstr ""
"WooCommerce slides yoo ṣe afihan awọn ọja rẹ laifọwọyi pẹlu awọn aworan, "
"ọrọ, awọn aaye aṣa, ati pupọ diẹ sii."

