msgid ""
"A modern slideshow theme with captions positioned at the top, showcasing "
"features with sleek elegance."
msgstr ""
"Ẹya ṣiṣan aworan igbalode pẹlu awọn akọsilẹ ti a gbe ni oke, ti n ṣafihan "
"awọn ẹya pẹlu ẹwa ti o rọrun."

