"aaye aiyẹsẹ ti o fa akiyesi olugbo."

#: themes/manifest-premium.php:71
msgid ""
"Best used with Image slides. It should also be used with Hidden Arrows, "
"Carousel Mode disabled, Transition Effect set to Slide, Smart Crop enabled "
"and Crop Source set to \"Custom width/height\"."
msgstr ""
"O dara julọ lati lo pẹlu awọn akọsilẹ Aworan. O yẹ ki o tun lo pẹlu Awọn "
"Arrow ti o farapamọ, ipo Carousel ti wa ni pipade, Ẹya Iyipada ti ṣeto si "
"Slide, Smart Crop ti wa ni mu ṣiṣẹ ati Ibi-orisun Crop ti ṣeto si "
"\"Iwọn/igbega aṣa\"."

